## Description {#details}

In-memory representation of the string table parsed from a buffer (e.g.

the remarks section).

Definition at line 60 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/remarks/remarkparser-h">RemarkParser.h</a>.
